    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100
        main.flex-shrink-0

            include includes/navbar.pug

            .v2-wrap

                //- Hero
                h1.v2-name Ali Bińkowska
                p.v2-belief-text(data-i18n='heroIntro') Hey, this is Ali. Welcome to my page.
                p.v2-belief-text(data-i18n='heroPara1') For every "no" there is a path to "yes" - I don't take dead ends at face value. I love building new things, especially when technology is the lever. If there's a smarter way to do something, I want to find it.
                p.v2-belief-text(data-i18n='heroPara2') I thrive in good collaboration and I'm equally comfortable pushing my own goals forward. I've built with public funding - now I'm focused on finding product-market fit for something I fully own.

                //- Roles & activities
                .v2-section
                    .v2-section-label(data-i18n='rolesLabel') Roles & activities

                    .v2-item
                        .v2-item-title
                            span.v2-dash —
                            span
                                span(data-i18n='role1Title') Solopreneur | Product Manager
                                |  &middot;
                                a(href='https://nexi8.pl' target='_blank') Nexi8
                        p.v2-item-desc(data-i18n='role1Desc') I help founders and business owners define goals, build metrics, and track what matters - through OKR sprints and Looker Studio dashboards.

                    .v2-item
                        .v2-item-title
                            span.v2-dash —
                            span(data-i18n='role2Title') Occasional AI Engineer
                        p.v2-item-desc(data-i18n='role2Desc') I work on optimisation projects with a focus on OCR, bots, and chatbots - building tools that extract, process, and automate.

                    .v2-item
                        .v2-item-title
                            span.v2-dash —
                            span
                                span(data-i18n='role3Title') AI Trainer
                                |  &middot;
                                a(href='https://paai.pl/o-nas' target='_blank') PAAI
                        p.v2-item-desc(data-i18n='role3Desc') I run AI training sessions helping teams and individuals work smarter with AI tools.

                    .v2-item
                        .v2-item-title
                            span.v2-dash —
                            span
                                span(data-i18n='role4Title') Guest Lecturer
                                |  &middot;
                                a(href='https://studia-online.pl/kadra/0/1417/mgr_alina_binkowska' target='_blank') WSKZ
                        p.v2-item-desc(data-i18n='role4Desc') Occasional guest lectures on AI, product thinking, and building in the modern tech landscape.

                //- Stack & tools
                .v2-section
                    .v2-section-label(data-i18n='stackLabel') Stack & tools
                    .v2-tags
                        span.v2-tag Claude Code
                        span.v2-tag Gemini
